

'''Wi-Mesh Alliance'''


URL = http://www.wi-mesh.org/


=Description=

"The Wi-Mesh Alliance is a group of companies with a common view towards rapidly achieving a complete and robust WLAN Mesh standard. The group has developed a proposal for IEEE 802.11s that enables the best trade-off between simplicity and performance. This proposal was developed under the guidelines of the IEEE Standards Association and submitted to the IEEE 802.11 Task Group S (TGs) in July 2005.

The alliance has a multi-national company profile representing a wide range of markets perspectives, just like the 802.11 WG."
(http://www.wi-mesh.org/)


